---
// Banner CTA final — claim + llamada a la acción
---

<section class="cta-banner px-6 py-28 md:py-36">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="label">¿Listo para crecer?</p>
    <h2 class="claim">
      Tu competencia ya está<br />invirtiendo en su marca.<br />
      <span class="accent">¿Y tú?</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="actions">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Hablemos de tu proyecto</a>
      <a href="/servicios" class="btn-ghost">Ver servicios →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-banner {
    background-color: var(--color-brand-yellow);
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-base-ink);
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .claim {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-base-ink);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .accent {
    opacity: 0.45;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .actions {
      flex-direction: row;
    }
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-base-ink);
    color: var(--color-base-bg);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-base-ink);
    color: var(--color-base-ink);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    background-color: rgba(25, 25, 25, 0.07);
  }
</style>
